= Story Guide =

'''Dragon Warrior II''' follows three descendants of Erdrick against the evil priest Hargon.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

A hundred years after the events of Dragon Warrior, the kingdom of Moonbrooke is destroyed by the evil priest Hargon. The Prince of Midenhall sets out to find his cousins and stop Hargon's conquest.

== Early Game ==

=== Midenhall Castle ===

Starting location:
# Speak with the King
# Learn of Moonbrooke's destruction
# Set out to find the Prince of Cannock

