== Finding the Princess of Moonbrooke ==

=== The Curse ===

The Princess of Moonbrooke was cursed into dog form when her kingdom fell.

=== Ra's Mirror ===

To restore her:
# Find the Ra's Mirror (swamp cave or tower)
# Travel to ruined Moonbrooke
# Find the dog wandering the ruins
# Use the Mirror on the dog
# Princess restored and joins party

=== Full Party ===

Now with three members:
* Prince of Midenhall (fighter)
* Prince of Cannock (hybrid)
* Princess of Moonbrooke (mage)

