== Boss Battles ==

=== Hargon ===

The evil priest:
* Multiple forms of magic
* Healing capability
* Defeat him to reveal true threat

=== Malroth ===

God of Destruction:
* Summoned after Hargon's defeat
* Extremely powerful
* True final boss

== Endings ==

After defeating Malroth:
* Peace restored
* Return to Midenhall
* Celebration of victory
* Credits roll

