== Tips ==

=== Grinding ===

* Metal Slimes give great EXP
* Midenhall area safe early
* Rhone plateau for endgame

=== Party Management ===

* Keep Princess safe (low HP)
* Cannock heals when needed
* Midenhall is tank

=== Spell Conservation ===

* Use physical attacks when possible
* Save Moonbrooke MP for bosses
* Herbs supplement healing

